Luis Suarez was spotted linking up with Lionel Messi and Neymar as Barcelona trained ahead of Monday's friendly.

The Uruguayan forward is now able to train with his new team-mates after the Court for Arbitration in Sport (CAS) ruled that FIFA did not have the powers to stop him.

Barcelona will face Mexican side Leon on Monday in their final pre-season game. they begin their La Liga campaign at home to Elche next weekend.

